# download Windows 10 iso from microsoft.com (64bit recommended)

# don't use Rufus! -> the GPT formatted UEFI USB Stick will not boot!
# Lenovo BIOS Updater require EFI only boot!

# download and install free version of Win2USB: https://www.easyuefi.com/wintousb/
#
# start Win2USB
# select your downloaded Windows 10 image
# select Windows 10 Home -> only option in free version!
# select your USB drive
# select GPT for UEFI !
# select yes to format your USB Stick
# install mode: Legacy !!!

# don't forget to copy the Lenovo BIOS Updater to your USB Stick !!!
# download driver from: https://pcsupport.lenovo.com/us/en/products/laptops-and-netbooks/5-series/ideapad-5-14alc05/downloads/driver-list/

# on your Lenovo Laptop
#
# Enter BIOS with F2:
# Boot/Boot Mode: UEFI
# Boot/USB Boot:  Enabled
# Security/Secure Boot: Disabled! (only visible if Boot/Boot Mode = UEFI)

# boot your EFI USB Stick (F12)
